{"tid":2292017,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銀主盤變樓王 天比高一幢值十億","createTime":"2020-11-19T07:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:28:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"079fb30655fc71d78dfe33db3af286e25e4b3b36","tid":2292017,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201119/GHIN7QFH4BHJHOWQYYSK5RY3EE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201119%2FGHIN7QFH4BHJHOWQYYSK5RY3EE%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=b3e2de43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201119%2FGHIN7QFH4BHJHOWQYYSK5RY3EE%2F&h=623e0e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201119/GHIN7QFH4BHJHOWQYYSK5RY3EE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銀主盤變樓王 天比高一幢值十億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ei_c4_ropb7w-jyK1xCdUy6TUrU=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RVNZX6KXEVAZNPDKA2SN3G7CSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEi_c4_ropb7w-jyK1xCdUy6TUrU%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRVNZX6KXEVAZNPDKA2SN3G7CSQ.jpg&h=f7a090f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周星馳與菱電購入天比高地皮後建成四幢大屋，每幢面積逾5,000方呎。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。，周星馳現持有12號屋，市值約十億。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年3月再承按<br />\n<br />\n和田一夫因財困，1996年把整座大屋以當時最高紀錄的3.7億元售予明珠興業創辦人黃坤。黃坤當時一心將天比高分拆成五幢獨立屋出售，未興建時已有單位獲「認頭」。惟1997年金融風暴淹至，黃坤身家暴跌，地皮淪為銀主盤還債。<br />\n<br />\n至2004年周星馳與菱電集團合作以3.2億元購入天比高地皮，重建成四幢獨立洋房，分別命名為普樂道10號、12號、16號及18號。洋房樓高四層半，俯瞰維港海景，實用面積5,119至5,989方呎，另有逾5,000方呎私家花園及泳池。<br />\n<br />\n10號、16號及18號三間大屋先後售出，2011年出售的10號屋造價達八億。周星馳保留12號大屋自用，傳聞有準買家不時出價洽購，卻未聞周割愛。周星馳2011年透過滙豐將12號屋承按，2019年贖回，今年3月疫情中再度承按。"},{"pid":"c7934cee8d3342b0c766188b09e5be9ec026a965","tid":2292017,"uid":221790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"講真周星星識春起樓咩，人地于文鳳用盡商界人脈同地產知識幫佢投地，拆卸，重建都係得𢭃兩皮一個月，咁撚孤寒"},{"pid":"48f612ec9f66588bf9d4ff94aad413fc550ec139","tid":2292017,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"有人肯接盤先得架...<br />\n冇人接盤你幢野吹到值幾多錢都係得個擺字"},{"pid":"b110c12f5dd6722fdd999fd4e2daaa0891ad068d","tid":2292017,"uid":199501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f612ec9f66588bf9d4ff94aad413fc550ec139","tid":2292017,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"有人肯接盤先得架...<br />\n冇人接盤你幢野吹到值幾多錢都係得個擺字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">10號、16號及18號三間大屋先後售出</span>，2011年出售的10號屋造價達八億。周星馳保留12號大屋自用<span class=\"red\">，傳聞有準買家不時出價洽購，卻未聞周割愛。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1ae8bb96377f5275978d1e56a4d187d70cd88041","tid":2292017,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"呢度咁多個接手，都係一接完就當黑，風水有啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70389c23213b5df3949f02a84a1500e05dca7b64","tid":2292017,"uid":59575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ae8bb96377f5275978d1e56a4d187d70cd88041","tid":2292017,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"呢度咁多個接手，都係一接完就當黑，風水有啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"用個天字 唔係咁易食得起"},{"pid":"037e1c720c1208611cf545ffbc813c0492a8b61e","tid":2292017,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70389c23213b5df3949f02a84a1500e05dca7b64","tid":2292017,"uid":59575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ae8bb96377f5275978d1e56a4d187d70cd88041","tid":2292017,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"呢度咁